  <brief_title>The Influence of Sensory Phenotype on the Risk of Developing Neuropathic Pain</brief_title>
  <official_title>DOLORisk: Understanding Risk Factors and Determinants for Neuropathic Pain - The Influence of Sensory Phenotype on the Risk of Developing Neuropathic Pain</official_title>
  <sponsors>
